      We should definitely eliminate the private banks power to create money out of thin air and loan it into existence at interest.  Money should be a public utility like electricity and water. An equitable distribution system would completely revive the economy towards more healthy, just, sustainable system.  The current system demands cancerous growth, not the healthy maturing of the economy to live within and in harmony with the biosphere.

                  
